thread.title: BRIEF-Zodiac Aerospace says Newport, WA facility is returning to operations
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Zodiac Aerospace says Newport, WA facility is returning to operations | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Zodiac Aerospace says Newport, WA facility is returning to operations
text:
Aug 7 Zodiac Aerospace SA :
* Gives update on situation following explosion at Zodiac Aerospace facility, located in Newport, WA, USA (occured July 14)
* Facility is returning to operations
* Investigation to determine cause of explosion is on-going
Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
